articles.body: AirDrop, which has been around for over a decade, is built into Apples software platforms, allowing for fast, wireless file transfers between iPhones, iPads and Macs. When it comes to sharing moments between family and friends, what device you have shouldnt matter sharing should just work, Google said in a surprise announcement on Thursday.
